Melody~
Melody the Herbalist~
Melody the herbalist stands here, filling out reciepts.
~
She is an overly cheerful sort of woman.  Very young still but in ownership
of this very shop.  She has long red hair tied back behind her shoulders,
dark green eyes, amd a small hint of greenness to match across her skin,
showing here to have very strong elven blood somewhat.  She looks up at
you while humming her songs, waiting for you to ask about buying something.
~
