mpat $n mpechoat $n  As the child dies, $j screams in agony every person turns toward you.  You're covered in blood on your hands and clothing.  Immediatly two guards rush up the road towards you, seizing you before you can even attempt escape..
mpat $n mpechoat $n One guard obviously sickened by this, lifts up his guantlet-clad hand in the air and brings it down upon your head.  Everything goes dark...
mpat $n mpechoaround $n The child gives a frightening scream as the life drains from $l body, killed by $n!  As soon as this happens, you see two guards run up the road to here, tackling $n to the ground.  One of them in an outburst of disgust towards this murder lifts up his gauntlet-clad fist, and brings it down upon $n's face.
mpat $n mpechoaround $n Thank goodness that $n won't be doing anything like this for a long time, $e is going to prison.
mpat $n mpmload 12413
mpat $n mpmload 12413
if ispc($n)
then
mptrans 0.$n 12458
else
mpforce $n mpgoto 12458
endif
mpat 12443 mpecho You see $n being dragged in by a guard, and thrown into the jail cell at the north of the room.  The Constable locks the door.
mpat 12443 mpmload 12413
mpat 12443 mpforce constable chat Attention citizens of New Hope: $n is a child murderer.  As of now $e has been locked up in prison, sentencing to be determined at a later time by the gods.
~
