#12444
guide book~
the tourist's guide to New Hope~
A book with the words "Look at me" written on the cover lies here.~
~
34 524288 1
0 0 0 0
1 0 0
E
'guide' 'book' 'tourist'~
Are you new to New Hope?  This is the guide for you!
 
Need refreshments?  Tasty meals prepared hot?  Just follow
the signs from town square (a.k.a. TSC) eastwards to the
New Hope Inn.
 
Or if you're planning on travelling out of town?  Then preservable
foods would probably be more appropriate.  If this is the case, try
coming to the New Hope Bakery, where we're more then just a bakery,
we sell everything for your fast food needs.
 
Supplies are a must for everyone, especially if you're going
to leave town for any amount of time.  At the General Store we
carry a wide range of items to supply you with everything you
need.  We're located in the southwestern corner of town, in the
gardens.
 
As long as you're in town, you'll want to do some shopping, right?
Come east of TSC to the three houses, where you'll find stores
for weapons, armor, equipment repairments, and jewelry.
 
Got some stuff you need to unload?  Need to make some quick
cash?  The pawn shop will buy your used equipment, and even sell
you anything that's come in from other people.  We're located
just next door to the bag shop on the east side of town.
 
Last of all, your time spent visiting New Hope couldn't be complete
without a visit to the infamous New Hope Castle, where the ruler
of this fine country resides in governing the city and lands.
Come north from the north gate through the great gardens until
you come to the drawbridge, and remember that the castle is open
only during the daytime.
 
  ---Payed for by the Kingdom of New Hope and the Amethyst Newbie Council.
~
