#12401
New Hope, at the Furrier's~
Standing here on the north side of town you feel odd shivers down you back.  In
this day and age there is sorts of danger most everywhere in most any form, and
the otherwise protective stone wall is broken apart here to your north, a
fallen wall.  To your south is the furrier's shop, marked by a rather small
building with a door to enter through to sell your pelts, skins, and hides.
~
