#12406
New Hope, at the Healer~
The road takes a little cut off from the wall for once and you stand just a
bit from it, along some bushes across the north side.  To the east is a single
building, which is the town healing shop.  Unlike the healing you recieve else-
where, this store mostly caters to the needs of clerics, and those who wish
to purchase the kinds of things clerics do such as potions to cure wounds.
Also to the south is the tavern, which you can enter just west from here.
