#12408
New Hope, at the Tavern~
Besides many bushes between you and the falling wall to the north, the only
thing right here is a tall, old building.  A large, faded sign on it reads
"Tavern", but it looks too worn and abandoned to be anything right now.
There is a door to the southeast leading into it, but that is completely
boarded up, so best not to go in there obviously.  Otherwise there is the
town brewery to the south, and the healing shop further down the road to
the east.
~
