#12412
New Hope, North of the West Gate~
You stand just to the north from the western gate.  From here you can see it
standing impenetrably, reinforced by the stone wall that comes from each of
its sides and surrounds the town, though you cannot see over this tall stone
wall.  To the east is the town well, source of water and such for the town, at
least that's what it used to do before it dried up...
