#12413
New Hope, at the town Well~
The road here ends from the west, and the ground is simply a dirt trail here
which circulates around a center well.  It is made of similar stone as that of
the town wall.  Once providing good water to the town's inhabitants, it has
since dried up in a very mysterious sort of way.  It is more of a landmark now
of some kind, just a reminder of the simpler days long ago, though not of any
real importance otherwise.
~
