#12458
Prison~
You are in a prison cell, in the town of New Hope.  To have gotten
here you must have done something wrong, and are now stuck here.
There are two ways to get out, you may either recieve a penalty or
may wait here to make your case to the next available immortal who
may find you here.
 
Realize that spamming channels or becoming an annoyance will only
get you into real trouble, resulting first in silencing, second
character deletion, and if necessary site ban.
 
Lastly your first time here is treated as a warning, if it was a
minor crime, and you will not have to take the penalty if you can
wait for an immortal to release you under your one && only warning.
~
0 1077322892 0 100
D2
~
door~
8651815 12593 12443
E
'board' 'crime' 'penalties'~
List of penalties:
+-----------------------------------------+--------------------------+
|                                         | 'I accept the penalty of |
| ----Stat Reductions----------------     |                          |
| Strength -1 point.                      | strength'                |
| Wisdom -1 point.                        | wisdom'                  |
| Constitution -1 point.                  | constitution'            |
| Dexterity -1 point.                     | dexterity'               |
| Intelligence -1 point.                  | intelligence'            |
|    (Only if you have 4+ and 18- of      |                          |
|    chosen stat.)                        |                          |
|                                         |                          |
| ----Experience---------------------     | ---------------------    |
| One player death, corpse is left alone. | death'                   |
|    (level 15+ only)                     |                          |
| Lose one level                          | level'                   |
|    (must be level 2+)                   |                          |
|                                         |                          |
| ----Money--------------------------     | ---------------------    |
| Lose all gold (Post Bail)               | gold'                    |
|    (300,000+ gold only)                 |                          |
|                                         |                          |
+-----------------------------------------+--------------------------+
Incurring a penalty _is_ an admission to guilt,
and therefor are under no circumstances
refundable or reversable.
For an example, should you choose to lose 1 strength, say
"I accept the penalty of strength".
~
> speech_prog p I accept the penalty of gold~
if goldamt($n) > 299999
mpat 12458 mptransfer $n 12481
mpat 12481 mpforce $n drop 300000 coins
mpat 12481 mptransfer $n 12458
mpat 12443 mpforce constable unlock door
mpat 12443 mpforce constable open door
mpat 12458 mpforce $n stand
mpat 12458 mpforce $n south
mpat 12443 mpforce constable close door
mpat 12443 mpforce constable lock door
mpat 12443 mpforce constable 'You're free $n...
mpat 12443 mpforce constable 'Be sure to keep out of trouble this time.
else
mpat 12458 mpecho You do not have enough money for that, $n.
endif
~
> speech_prog p I accept the penalty of death~
mpat 12458 mpecho Your execution will proceed at once, $n
mpat 12458 mpecho May the gods have mercy on your soul.
mpat 12458 mptransfer $n 25
mpat 12443 mpforce constable mpat 25 'The prisoner is ready to be executed.
mpat 25 mpforce executioner 'Are you ready to die, $n?
~
|
